  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>La Terrazza at Belmond Hotel Splendido</strong> is open for lunch and dinner and serves regional specialities in a spectacular setting overlooking Portofino’s bay. Lunch is served from 1:00-2:30pm and dinner is served from 7:30-10:30pm. </p>
<p><strong>Chuflay Restaurant at Belmond Splendido Mare</strong> recreates a glamorous past with an authentic setting and Italian cuisine. Guests can enjoy breakfast from 7:30 - 10:30am, Lunch from 12:30 - 3:30pm and Dinner from 7:30 - 11:00pm. </p>
<p><strong>Pool Restaurant</strong> is open from spring to autumn and serves casual fare in an incredible buffet and freshly-made pizzas. The Restaurant is open from 1:00pm -4:00pm and the bar is open from 10am - 7:00pm.</p>
<p><strong>Gelateria San Giorgio</strong> offers a large choice of delicious flavours of ice cream that can be enjoyed on the towns vibrant piazetta. Open from 9:00am - 12:00pm. </p>
<p><strong>Cocktail Bar at Belmond Hotel Splendido</strong> is open between 10:00am and 1:00am and is a lovely, sophisticated place where you can enjoy a drink. Head over in the evening for nightcap whilst listening to the melodic tunes of the resident pianist. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel’s heated sea-water pool is surrounded by gardens and looks out over the bay.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Complimentary shuttle to central Portofino</li>
<li>Fitness centre</li>
<li>Tennis courts</li>
<li>Free wifi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
