  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sea View Rooms </strong>are about 20m² and have beautiful ocean views from the window. The rooms have a comfortable King-sized or twin beds. Facilities include air conditioning, wifi, minibar, and TV. Rooms with a balcony are available for a supplement. </p>
<p><strong>Garden View Rooms</strong> have been finished in an elegant style and enjoy large windows with views over the hotel’s lush gardens. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Junior Suites</strong> have plenty of space and a lovely seating area. They all enjoy sea views and some have a small balcony. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Junior Suites</strong> enjoy magnificent views over the gulf and a furnished balcony or terrace. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Executive Junior Suites</strong> have hardwood floors and a natural style. Each one comes with a furnished terrace with sea views. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are also available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
